    "description": "<strong>For video creators and streamers</strong><br>KIMIDORI SOFT permits monetization through partner programs using KIMIDORI SOFT games.<br><br>Who doesn't love yakiniku?<br><br>How much can you eat at the BBQ restaurant? How many days can you survive at the BBQ restaurant? How far can your stomach endure? Who grilled this meat anyway? Food waste is a no-go.<br><br>Stealing, being stolen from, sometimes giving, and the budding friendships... all with a tear in your eye.<br><br>Welcome to Yakiniku Party Survival.<br><br><strong>Game Overview:</strong><br>Survive by consuming a balanced mix of protein, carbohydrates, and fats.<br>Each ingredient affects your nutritional balance differently.<br>If you overeat and your calories go overboard, you won’t be able to eat anymore. Burn off those calories with squats!<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br>Online Multiplayer: Play with up to 4 people. Both Quick Matches and Friend Matches are available, and you can freely enter or leave either. In Quick Matches, survivors from around the world play at their own pace. Friend Matches let you easily play with specific friends using a single keyword. Of course, you can also play solo.<br><br>Cooperative or Competitive Play: In online multiplayer, you can grill meat for other players or steal their meat instead.<br><br>Skills: Learn and upgrade survival skills, such as tableware, rice, stomach expansion, or squat efficiency.<br><br>Fever Event: During The Fever event, no matter how much you consume, it’s zero calories! It’s your chance to balance your nutrition in one go.",
